approx_log_fac <- function(n){ 
    a <- n*log(n) - n + log(pi*(1+4*pi*(1+2*n)))/6 + log(pi)/2
    a
}

tpoisson_ll <- function(param, data) {
  alpha <- param[1]
  beta <- param[2]
  m <- as.matrix(data$m)
  n <- as.matrix(data$n)
  N <- as.matrix(data$N)
  mu <- N^alpha*(n/N)^beta
  res <- dtpois(x = m, lambda = mu, log = T, a = 0)
  #res <- -mu + m*log(mu)
  res
}

t2poisson_ll <- function(param, data) {
  alpha <- param[1]
  beta <- param[2]
  m <- as.matrix(data$m)
  n <- as.matrix(data$n)
  N <- as.matrix(data$N)
  mu <- N^alpha*(n/N)^beta
  res <- dtpois(x = m, lambda = mu, log = T, a = 1)
  #res <- -mu + m*log(mu)
  res
}

Negative binomial

negbin_ll <- function(param, data) {
  alpha <- param[1]
  beta <- param[2]
  phi <- param[3]
  m <- as.matrix(data$m)
  n <- as.matrix(data$n)
  N <- as.matrix(data$N)
  mu <- N^alpha*(n/N)^beta
  res <- dnbinom(x = m, size = phi, mu = mu, log = T)
  res
}
negbin_ll <- function(param, data) {
  alpha <- param[1]
  beta <- param[2]
  phi <- param[3]
  m <- as.matrix(data$m)
  n <- as.matrix(data$n)
  N <- as.matrix(data$N)
  mu <- N^alpha*(n/N)^beta
  res <- lgamma(m+phi^-1) - lgamma(phi^-1) - approx_log_fac(m) - (m + phi^-1)*log(1+phi*mu) + m*log(phi*mu) 
  res
}
